{"tid":2202964,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［偽出國］各國航空公司疫情下新服務一覽","createTime":"2020-09-15T04:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T06:36:42.000Z","uid":48124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"876a9b572fac509af5178ed22508abb47add3fb2","tid":2202964,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"2020大概是航空公司有史以來最寒冬的時刻，之前跟大家分享過數十間的航空公司已經宣布破產倒閉。<br />\n<br />\n而現存活的航空公司為了生存，有哪些因應疫情而生的做法呢？<br />\n<br />\n#南極觀光：<br />\n<br />\n澳洲航空（Qantas）：南極觀光之旅，與南極洲航空公司合作，預計今年11月推出，飛機將不降落但可看到南極冰帽之美。<br />\n<br />\n＃過夜包販售：<br />\n<br />\n澳洲航空：販售頂級過夜包，25澳幣，裡面有12片巧克力餅干、一套睡衣、和原本只提供給頭等艙旅客吃的一款煙燻杏仁果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#在家吃飛機餐系列：<br />\n<br />\nAir North；飛機餐外送到府的服務，菜單商品包括9加幣（6.88美元）的牛肉派、和13加幣的嚴選乳酪蛋糕。<br />\n<br />\n泰航：在曼谷開設一間由飛機配件與座椅打造的餐廳。<br />\n<br />\n#偽出國系列：<br />\n<br />\nANA: 採用A380海龜機在東京上空盤旋90分鐘，空服員也穿夏威夷打扮並提供雞尾酒，價格約日幣14000元。<br />\n<br />\n星宇/長榮：皆提供偽出國行程。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡航空：即將推出3小時fly to nowhere 行程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#出租辦公室：<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭航空：考慮出租奧克蘭總部的部分空間，六層樓高的紐航總部辦公室，有多達25%的空間打算開放外界租用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#水果蔬菜配送：<br />\n<br />\n AirAsia：推出Outfarm的電商平台，販售各式各樣新鮮蔬果，運用該公司原有的貨運、運籌和支付體系，讓當地的農民可直接接觸到飯店、餐廳和超市等通路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#飛行吃到飽：<br />\n<br />\n中國東方航空：在12月31日之前，以3,322元(485美元)的價格，無限次乘坐周末航班。兩個禮拜約有超過15萬人使用該通行證，某些航班使用率高於90%。<br />\n<br />\nSource <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/339793543065536/posts/1188292118215670/?extid=0DscaUHArQUOKCDG&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F339793543065536%2Fposts%2F1188292118215670%2F%3Fextid%3D0DscaUHArQUOKCDG%26d%3Dn&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=2ad76a5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/339793543065536/posts/1188292118215670/?extid=0DscaUHArQUOKCDG&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"7bb1dd5abd20e7b4bf3131c212aad662dfa1f189","tid":2202964,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:23:12.000Z","msg":"staycation 飛機版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d768f20a576e65c73012d272430cf0ce9ee5525","tid":2202964,"uid":81368,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:35:40.000Z","msg":"點解國泰唔搞<br />\n明明好多人都會比錢join <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41eba2cdb78e15f8af08db414779d61437a0938f","tid":2202964,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d768f20a576e65c73012d272430cf0ce9ee5525","tid":2202964,"uid":81368,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:35:40.000Z","msg":"點解國泰唔搞<br />\n明明好多人都會比錢join <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"就算express攪都會大把人參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d21620e4d8516b34f09003b24fc417c8812451b","tid":2202964,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"咁CX不如同海洋公園合作搞個飛機機動遊戲嘛"},{"pid":"641be0994b5b7186deeb150dff4180b7e3b7ef61","tid":2202964,"uid":60145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:36:42.000Z","msg":"因航可以係機上搞篤灰遊戲"}]}